# Brace Style

Always use curly braces for control-flow bodies, even when the body is a single statement.

```js
// ❌ BAD
if (condition) doSomething();
if (condition)
  doSomething();

// ✅ GOOD
if (condition) {
  doSomething();
}
```

Applies to `if`, `else`, `else if`, `for`, `while`, and `do…while`.
